## 주요 타입

```typescript
interface Block {
  index: number;
  timestamp: number;
  transactions: Transaction[];
  previousHash: string;
  hash: string;
  nonce: number;
}

interface Chain {
  blocks: Block[];
  difficulty: number;
  pendingTransactions: Transaction[];
}

interface Transaction {
  from: string;
  to: string;
  amount: number;
  timestamp?: number;
}

interface MerkleTree {
  tree: string[][];
  root: string;
}
```

---

## 완전한 예제

```typescript
import { Blockchain } from 'freelang-v4';

// 1. 체인 생성
const chain = Blockchain.createChain(3);

// 2. 트랜잭션 생성
const tx1 = Blockchain.createTransaction('Alice', 'Bob', 50);
const tx2 = Blockchain.createTransaction('Bob', 'Charlie', 30);

// 3. 블록 생성 및 채굴
let block = Blockchain.createBlock(0, [tx1, tx2], '0');
block = Blockchain.mineBlock(block, 3);

// 4. 블록 검증
const isValid = Blockchain.isValidBlock(block, '0');
console.log(`Block valid: ${isValid}`);

// 5. 체인에 추가
Blockchain.addBlock(chain, block);

// 6. 체인 검증
const chainValid = Blockchain.getChainValid(chain);
console.log(`Chain valid: ${chainValid}`);

// 7. Merkle Tree
const tree = Blockchain.createMerkleTree([tx1, tx2]);
console.log(`Merkle root: ${tree.root}`);
```

